    <chapter>
        <title>XML Validation</title>
        <section id="sect1">
            <title>Introduction</title>
            <para>The database supports validation of XML in two different ways. The first one is automagic 
                validation of XML documents while they are inserted into the database, the second way is validation
                of XML documents (either stored in database or in constructed memory) using an xquery extension 
                function. </para>
        </section>
